name: Cashier Summary Report
query:
select
'Opening'  as "Type:Data:200",
0 as "Total Billing:Currency,100",
(select (sum(debit)-sum(credit)) cashbalance from `tabGL Entry` where posting_date < %(date)s and account in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(cashmod)s and company=%(company)s) ) as "Cash:Currency:100",

(select (sum(debit)-sum(credit)) chequebalance from `tabGL Entry` where posting_date < %(date)s and account in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(chequemod)s and company=%(company)s) )   as "Cheque:Currency:100",

(select (sum(debit)-sum(credit)) creditbalance from `tabGL Entry` where posting_date < %(date)s and account in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(creditmod)s and company=%(company)s) )    as "Credit Card:Currency:100" ,
(sum(debit)-sum(credit) ) as "Total Allocation:Currency:100"
from `tabGL Entry` 
 where posting_date < %(date)s and account in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)

union

select 
'Cash IN (Same Day)',
(select sum(tso.rounded_total) from `tabSales Order` tso where tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s) as totalbilling ,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s 
and (tper.reference_name in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 or reference_name in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))
 ))  as cash,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and (tper.reference_name in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 or reference_name in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))
 ))   as cheque,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and (tper.reference_name in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 or reference_name in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))
 ))  as creditcard,
 sum(Allocated_amount) as totalallocation
from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Receive' and tpe.docstatus=1 and (tper.reference_name in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 or reference_name in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))
 )

union

select 'Cash Out (Same Day)',
(select sum(ts.grand_total) from `tabSales Invoice` ts  where ts.is_return=1 and ts.docstatus=1 and ts.posting_date = %(date)s and %(cost_center)s in (select tsi.cost_center from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.parent=ts.name))  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where payment_type='Pay' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tper.reference_name  in (select ts.return_against from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))  as `Cash`,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where payment_type='Pay' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tper.reference_name  in (select ts.return_against from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))  as `Cheque`,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where payment_type='Pay' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tper.reference_name  in (select ts.return_against from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))  as `Credit`,
 sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Pay' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tper.reference_name  in (select ts.return_against from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s )

union

select 'Pending Cash Received',
(0)  as `Bill Amount`,
(select (ifnull(sum(allocated_amount),0)+ ifnull(sum(unallocated_amount),0))  from `tabPayment Entry` tpe left join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where tpe.payment_type='Receive' and tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s 
and  (tper.reference_name not in  ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 and reference_name not in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s )) ))   as `Cash`,

(select (sum(Allocated_amount)+sum(unallocated_amount)) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe left join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where tpe.payment_type='Receive' and tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s 
and  (tper.reference_name not in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 and reference_name not in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))
 ))   as `Cheque`,
(select (ifnull(sum(allocated_amount),0)+ ifnull(sum(unallocated_amount),0)) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe left join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where tpe.payment_type='Receive' and tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s 
and  (tper.reference_name not in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 and reference_name not in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))  ))   as `Credit`,

(ifnull(sum(allocated_amount),0)+ ifnull(sum(unallocated_amount),0)) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe left join `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Receive' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  (tper.reference_name not in ( select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s  )
 and reference_name not in (select distinct(tsi.parent) from `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi where tsi.sales_order in (select name from `tabSales Order` tso where docstatus=1 and tso.transaction_date = %(date)s and tso.cost_center=%(cost_center)s )) ) 
and tpe.paid_to in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s) 

union

select 'Pending Cash Out',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where payment_type='Pay' and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tper.reference_name  not in (select ifnull(ts.return_against,0) from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))  as `Cash`,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where payment_type='Pay' and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tper.reference_name  not in (select ifnull(ts.return_against,0) from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s )) as `Cheque`,
(select sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join  `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent  where payment_type='Pay' and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tper.reference_name  not in (select ifnull(ts.return_against,0) from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s ))  as `Credit`,
 sum(Allocated_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` tper on tpe.name=tper.parent 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Pay' and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tper.reference_name not in (select ifnull(ts.return_against,0) from `tabSales Invoice` ts inner join `tabSales Invoice Item` tsi on ts.name=tsi.parent  where  ts.posting_date = %(date)s and tsi.cost_center=%(cost_center)s )
and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)

union

select 'Credit Card Charges',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(tpd.amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Deduction` tpd on tpe.name=tpd.parent where payment_type='Receive' and party!='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s )*-1  as `Cash`,
(select sum(tpd.amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Deduction` tpd on tpe.name=tpd.parent where payment_type='Receive' and party!='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s)*-1   as `Cheque`,
(select sum(tpd.amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Deduction` tpd on tpe.name=tpd.parent where payment_type='Receive' and party!='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s )*-1  as `Credit`,
 sum(tpd.amount)*-1  from `tabPayment Entry` tpe inner join `tabPayment Entry Deduction` tpd on tpe.name=tpd.parent
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Receive'  and party!='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 
and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)

union

select 'GL Payment Receive',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Receive' and party_type='Customer' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s )  as `Cash`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Receive' and party_type='Customer' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s)  as `Cheque`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Receive' and party_type='Customer' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s ) as `Credit`,
 sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Receive' and party_type='Customer' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 
and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)

union

select 'GL Payment Paid',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Pay' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s )*-1  as `Cash`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Pay'  and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s)*-1  as `Cheque`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Pay' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and company=%(company)s and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s )*-1 as `Credit`,
 sum(paid_amount)*-1 from `tabPayment Entry` tpe 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Pay' and party='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 
and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)


union

select 'Supplier & Expense Payments',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Pay' and party!='GL Payment' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(cashmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s  and tpe.company = %(company)s and tpe.name not in (select pe.name from `tabPayment Entry` pe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` per on pe.name=per.parent  where  pe.posting_date = %(date)s and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' )  )*-1  as `Cash`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Pay' and party!='GL Payment' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(chequemod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.company = %(company)s and tpe.name not in (select pe.name from `tabPayment Entry` pe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` per on pe.name=per.parent  where  pe.posting_date = %(date)s and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' ) )*-1  as `Cheque`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Pay' and party!='GL Payment' and  tpe.mode_of_payment=%(creditmod)s and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.company = %(company)s and tpe.name not in (select pe.name from `tabPayment Entry` pe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` per on pe.name=per.parent  where  pe.posting_date = %(date)s and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' ) )*-1  as `Credit`,
 sum(paid_amount)*-1 from `tabPayment Entry` tpe 
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Pay' and party!='GL Payment' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s) and tpe.name not in (select pe.name from `tabPayment Entry` pe inner join `tabPayment Entry Reference` per on pe.name=per.parent  where  pe.posting_date = %(date)s and reference_doctype='Sales Invoice' )

union

select 'Outward Transfers',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(cashmod)s and company=%(company)s) )*-1  as `Cash`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(chequemod)s and company=%(company)s) )*-1  as `Cheque`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(creditmod)s and company=%(company)s) )*-1  as `Credit`,
 sum(paid_amount)*-1 from `tabPayment Entry` tpe
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1
 and tpe.paid_from in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)

union

select 'Inward Transfers',
0  as `Bill Amount`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.paid_to in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(cashmod)s and company=%(company)s) )  as `Cash`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.paid_to in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(chequemod)s and company=%(company)s) )  as `Cheque`,
(select sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe where payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1 and tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.paid_to in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent=%(creditmod)s and company=%(company)s) )  as `Credit`,
 sum(paid_amount) from `tabPayment Entry` tpe
 where tpe.posting_date=%(date)s and tpe.payment_type='Internal Transfer' and tpe.docstatus=1
 and tpe.paid_to in (select default_account from `tabMode of Payment Account` where parent in (%(cashmod)s,%(chequemod)s,%(creditmod)s) and company=%(company)s)
